ITV Tonight Ebola: Are We Prepared?

Health-Medical, Science Documentary hosted by Alok Jha, published by ITV Tonight in 2014 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

Ebola: Are We Prepared?
ITV News science correspondent Alok Jha reports on how the UK plans to protect itself from an outbreak of the deadly disease, which has recently claimed over 3,000 lives worldwide. He examines the screening measures being considered in major shipping ports and airports and asks how hospitals and health services are gearing up to fight the potential epidemic. While vaccination trials are currently underway in Oxford, a cure is still unavailable

